## Formatting Requirements

Script follows professional podcast formatting standards:
- Header metadata in standardized format with all required fields
- Content organized with clear visual hierarchy (H1-H3 headings)
- Delivery cues using consistent notation and placement
- Production cues clearly distinguished from script content
- Accessibility features integrated throughout document

